Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:15.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:26.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:33.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:47.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:55.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:03:03.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:11.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:19.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:25.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:15.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:26.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:33.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊繫過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:47.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:55.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:03:03.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:11.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:19.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:25.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在漣漪的水面深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映著蔚藍的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未來又將飄零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季節長存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們編織命運之絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻從來都不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這絲線將通向何處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(僅僅佇立於此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每當我與他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靈感乍現時的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已經隱約察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終會有結束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終有漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好時光關入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不過我會在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}寫下一句「我沒事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾一定能夠實現乃乃香的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  小春  水坂君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有戶川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  妳看妳看都到齊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到齊啦  到齊啦  到齊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我有些話一定想要跟大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天黑之前  最好能先下山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對  先跟老師們匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文臺的事情  一直跟大家玩耍的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連再見也沒有說的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…召喚飛碟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了  那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為這樣就可以得到原諒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:01:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:36.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(32,270)}「思念的碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾以為  大家聚集在一起就能實現乃乃香的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  好像行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是諾艾爾弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  願望是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  乃乃香也要打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  穿成那樣不要出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天漂亮利索地打了雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得爸爸做一次料理  涼了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我要出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點話想跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是乃乃香的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  不打算原諒她也不打算向她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想好好談一談乃乃香的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春叫過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不說  一個人消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道因為這只飛碟  這裡都發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我才想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鎮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有必須要去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要去做同一件事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把飛碟趕出去  一個人就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟  乃乃香  小春  湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  我還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太  你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從學校回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想要是離得不遠的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你談一談柚季的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我沒能好好說出來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太為柚季的事煩心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士來了  下次再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是飛碟的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水坂君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
