Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到您的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家同心協力把飛碟趕走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把飛碟從小鎮上趕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
