Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加  油  咯
